column5: Will be spending the middle 2 weeks in July on Lac Seul staying at Gold Pines camp. Looking forward to meeting and talking fishing with anyone on here who's going to be there at the same time.
We'll be there the 15-22nd, stop by to have a beer! Bill, helen, Peter & Christa will show you who we are. Tom
Do you what cabin you'll be in ? I'll be with the wife and a red & white Starcraft with an ETEC
